thread.title: Pat Thorpe
thread.title_full: Ink Station reviewed by Pat Thorpe

author: Pat Thorpe
title: Pat Thorpe
text: I have ordered through Ink Station before. This time the goods arrived within 24 hours whereas previously it had taken some weeks. It is great to have the tracking number, as my goods are going to Cape York and items are often not found. What was unique about this delivery was the speed of delivery.
